{"title":"Ornot Magic Shell Jacket for Men and Women","link":"https://theradavist.com/ornot-magic-shell-jacket-for-men-and-women/","date":1738245644000,"content":"<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Ornot_MagicShell_Jacket_StoneBlue_Squares-2.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Ornot_MagicShell_Jacket_StoneBlue_Squares-2.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Ornot_MagicShell_Jacket_StoneBlue_Squares-2.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Ornot_MagicShell_Jacket_StoneBlue_Squares-2.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p><em>Breathability and multiple-condition riding is what <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/tag/ornot/\" target=\"_blank\">Ornot</a> was going for with its new Polartec Power Shield <a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;merchant_id=34a711d0-83d2-4a96-8e01-9f5ea4abd1fc&amp;website_id=6ec3743b-a948-4c16-9d12-4b79ac107f25&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ornotbike.com%2Fcollections%2Fmagic-shell-jackets\" target=\"_blank\">Magic Shell jacket</a> ($285)…</em><span></span></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Ornot_Womens_MagicShell_Jacket_StoneBlue_Squares-3.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Ornot_Womens_MagicShell_Jacket_StoneBlue_Squares-3.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Ornot_Womens_MagicShell_Jacket_StoneBlue_Squares-3.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Ornot_Womens_MagicShell_Jacket_StoneBlue_Squares-3.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Ornot_Mens_MagicShell_Jacket_StoneBlue_Squares-1.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Ornot_Mens_MagicShell_Jacket_StoneBlue_Squares-1.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Ornot_Mens_MagicShell_Jacket_StoneBlue_Squares-1.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Ornot_Mens_MagicShell_Jacket_StoneBlue_Squares-1.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>This innovative fabric is breathable enough for use as an everyday cycling jacket, and when you add bonded and taped seams paired with new rear pockets and two-layer cuffs, you have the only outer layer needed to enjoy year-round riding, no matter what Mother Nature has in store.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Ornot_Mens_MagicShell_Jacket_StoneBlue_Hero-1.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Ornot_Mens_MagicShell_Jacket_StoneBlue_Hero-1.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Ornot_Mens_MagicShell_Jacket_StoneBlue_Hero-1.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Ornot_Mens_MagicShell_Jacket_StoneBlue_Hero-1.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>The Magic Shell is made in California, the soft and stretchy fabric allows easy layering from 55 to 32 degrees and has a two-way YKK zipper for temperature regulation on the bike. Wear it all the time, Ornot.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Ornot_Mens_MagicShell_Jacket_StoneBlue_01.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Ornot_Mens_MagicShell_Jacket_StoneBlue_01.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Ornot_Mens_MagicShell_Jacket_StoneBlue_01.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Ornot_Mens_MagicShell_Jacket_StoneBlue_01.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Ornot_Womens_MagicShell_Jacket_StoneBlue_02.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Ornot_Womens_MagicShell_Jacket_StoneBlue_02.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Ornot_Womens_MagicShell_Jacket_StoneBlue_02.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Ornot_Womens_MagicShell_Jacket_StoneBlue_02.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p><strong>Specs:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Extremely breathable microporous hydrophobic membrane.</li>\n<li>Perfect from 55 degrees to below freezing with appropriate layers.</li>\n<li>Bonded and taped seams</li>\n<li>99% windproof and waterproof</li>\n<li>Updated 2-layer Cuff</li>\n<li>Stretchy and Quiet – Doesn’t flap in the wind</li>\n<li>Constructed with bluesign®-approved materials, which conserve resources and protect the environment’s health, workers, and you.</li>\n<li>YKK 2-way double zipper.</li>\n<li>255 grams (size small).</li>\n<li>Size-specific rear pockets, secure zipper pocket</li>\n<li>Low-key reflective detailing on front and back.</li>\n<li>PFAS Free DWR coating + bluesign®-approved fabric.</li>\n<li>Made in California!</li>\n<li>MSRP: $285</li>\n</ul>\n<p>See more at <a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;merchant_id=34a711d0-83d2-4a96-8e01-9f5ea4abd1fc&amp;website_id=6ec3743b-a948-4c16-9d12-4b79ac107f25&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ornotbike.com%2Fcollections%2Fmagic-shell-jackets\" target=\"_blank\">Ornot</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/ornot-magic-shell-jacket-for-men-and-women/\">Ornot Magic Shell Jacket for Men and Women</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"11eece97e65bcbcc1a1196be01e1ae85f607d5b3a785cdf23120fb7a587fdca3","category":"Cycling"}